---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
	<p>
		Hello, I'm Quentin, a being passionated by Live Action Role Playing
		games, Burning Man-like events, performing arts, and sciences.
	</p>
	<p>
		My goal here is to make organizations able to create the best working
		environments and get the best of the people to be able to build the
		right solutions with high quality.
	</p>

	<p>
		As each context is different, there is no one-solution-fits-all. The
		approach is the solution:
		<ul>
			<li>
				<b>Agnostic &#X2500;</b> An approach driven by the mindsets goes
				beyond the one driven by the tools
			</li>
			<li>
				<b>Tailored-made &#X2500;</b> The people and the organization make
				their own solutions
			</li>
			<li>
				<b>Hands-on &#X2500;</b> Creating is a process of trial and failure,
				only allowed by doing
			</li>
		</ul>
	</p>

	<p>
		My values are central in my approach:
		<ul>
			<li>
				<b>Human &#X2500;</b> Individuals and their interactions make organizations
			</li>
			<li>
				<b>Trust &#X2500;</b> Collaboration creates great things when based
				on trust
			</li>
			<li>
				<b>Simplicity &#X2500;</b> Everyone in the organization should be
				able to understand how it works
			</li>
		</ul>
	</p>

	<p>
