		and individuals. The will to change is more important than anything
		else! To this end, my offer includes:
		<ul>
			<li>Coaching</li>
			<li>Practical and theoretical trainings</li>
			<li>Workshops</li>
			<li>Facilitation</li>
		</ul>
	</p>

	<p>
		I mainly focus on Agile, Lean, Design Thinking, and self-organization
		which include different tools and frameworks: eXtreme Programming,
		Scrum, Kanban, Holacracy, Objectives & Key Results, User Story Mapping,
		... All together they are the toolbox I take with me for every mission.
